

When the website is not responding how to troubleshoot or debug network issue

01.) ping www.google.com

02.) traceroute www.google.com

03.) netstat -a - check server talking with how many servers

04.) nmap -p 1-1000 target (p=port)

05.) tcpdump -i eth0 (monitoring)

06.) ipconfig (windows) or ifconfig(linux)

07.) dig www.google.com (domain information groper)

08.) nslookup (windows) or host (linux)

